    "# Reassessment — execution_01 with 03c surfaces + 07e sxy in hand\n",
    "\n",
    "**Date:** 2026-04-24  \n",
    "**Scope:** reassess the `full_automatic_execution_01` findings given three artefacts that were not available to those sessions:\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **CZ pia + HCR top + HCR bottom surfaces** (session 03c, iter07/iter08) — cached under `code/dev_code/cached_surfaces/`.\n",
    "2. **sxy from per-cell ROI-area ratio** (session 07e, promoted to `code/dev_code/roi_area_sxy.py`) — 788406 err −1.6 %, 790322 err +1.2 %.\n",
    "3. **Shared convention**: scale + translation priors can now be *pinned* rather than estimated from centroid positions alone.\n",
    "\n",
    "Two \"good\" subjects per the data-description testing priorities: **788406** and **790322**. Companion markdown: `reassessment.md`. Driver: `compute_diagnostics.py`."
   ]
