   "source": [
    "## 3. Which failed execution_01 methods change tier\n",
    "\n",
    "Cross-reference against the failed-methods list in session 61. For each, mark whether the priors (sxy pin, HCR-pia Z anchor, sz interval) remove the documented failure cause.\n",
    "\n",
    "| method | execution_01 verdict | root cause | new verdict |\n",
    "|---|---|---|---|\n",
    "| **P3 — RANSAC affine** | near-zero | 7-DOF under-determined | **unblocks** — 3-DOF (R-fine, t_xy) |\n",
    "| **P5 — FGW** | collapsed | CZ/HCR distances not µm-matched | **revival plausible** (pre-scale by sxy) |\n",
    "| **M1 — mask density NCC** | density mismatch | unknown scale | **reconsider** — density matchable |\n",
    "| **M3 — mask warm-start + centroid** | warm-start too weak | −26 % sz ⇒ >200 µm Z offset | **reconsider** — t_z pinned ±50 µm |\n",
    "| **M4 — per-cell overlap** | CZ outline-only | orthogonal data issue | **still blocked** |\n",
    "| **I1 — depth intensity profile** | 1-D only | info content | **stays neutral** |\n",
    "| **I2 — 3D MI affine** | weak warm-start | scale unfindable by MI alone | **reconsider as refiner** |\n",
    "| **I3 — MI + B-spline** | overshoots | B-spline absorbed affine | **unblocks** — affine locked |\n",
    "| **G1 / G2 — learned matcher** | synthetic → real gap | representation, not geometry | **still blocked** |\n",
    "| **B1 / B2 — seed + TPS** | no reliable seed | — | **partially** — sxy improves seeds |\n",
    "| **C1 — image warm-start + P1** | no gain | image warm-start ≈ ICP | **supersedes** — priors *are* C1's role |\n",
    "\n",
    "**Net:** priors pin 3 of 7 affine DOF. Four methods unblock (P3, P5, M1, I3), one reconsiders (M3), three stay blocked for reasons orthogonal to geometry (G1/G2/M4/I1)."
   ]
